rows.label: tlk45500152_02_msg0001
rows.name:
Okay, who's been messing around
with my stuff while I was asleep?!

rows.label: tlk45500152_02_msg0002
rows.name:
The boxes I stacked up for
maximum efficiency are a
whole ped out of line!

rows.label: tlk45500152_02_msg0003
rows.name:
The imperial soldiers were
causing a ruckus during the
night, weren't they?

rows.label: tlk45500152_02_msg0004
rows.name:
Defending the peace of the capital
is all very well, but I wish they'd
consider our livelihoods as well!

rows.label: tlk45500152_02_msg0005
rows.name:
We don't pay all that tax
for nothing, you know!
